title: [Warrior Guild, Eastern Grove]
description: Tall, unshorn grass accompanied by a wide variety of trees fills this portion of the grove.  A trio of young apple trees planted in a triangular fashion look to be a few seasons shy of providing fruit.  A bit of sunlight manages to filter through the heavy cover, but it is losing the battle.
